reviewText: lots of good movies on this dvd set and must see for all movie lovers out there
Received as expected.
I have no words to say, I love all action pack movies.  This 8 pack keep me on my toes over the weekend, it was rainly and have this many movies to watch took up my time.

the first DVD made me feel cold, what having been born in Vermont, growing up/living there, then moving to Montana where I also grew up and lived, COLD, is NOT something I like, I live in Texas for right now, it gets cold here too, but not as severe, the 2ND DVD was heart wrenching and enlightens the viewer about human trafficking, it's real, and happens
Some of the movies and definitely B movies. Not a bad value for your money if you want to add to your collection.
Worth the money if you're looking for movies to watch to kill the time.  Some good some bad based on my subjective preferences.
Not to much to say here, the movies were something to watch on a cold day. No great shakes but better than some.
I am aging,now enjoy more family style movies..others would enjoy and there are 8 to choose from.  Bargain  price choices
The price is excellent for good action packed movies. The movies are fun to watch while working out my treadmill or elliptical machine.  The workout time seems to go by faster and I feel better.
this is something i really love i seen it on tv now i get to see this any time i want i am glad that i ran acoss it

some of the movies were really good while I could see others were just fillers for the box to have 8 films. as I fast forewarded through one. but all in all some entertainment and very good photography.

Only one disk and 4 movies were included, I returned the item so obviously I wasn't too happy with the purchase.
The video quality wasn't too good but they were older low budget movies so that's expected to a degree.
I have purchased other multi-movie disks and been satisfied considering the cost.

I wish when I first started my collection I was able to collect this. Anyway, it is not too late now that I have found a cheaper way.
The films are great. I enjoyed every one.
Thank you Amazon!
My family and I are enjoying the movies on this video.  Since we cancelled our cable, they provide many hours of entertainment at a great price.

I have no way of knowing how good or bad the movies are, but the product itself is of no value to me.  Even with both hearing aids properly set, I could neither access English subtitles from the shows, nor closed captioning from my own monitor.  Pretty much worthless sums it up.  And, of course, no way to return it for credit.

Kurt A.
My husband and I love action/adventure movies and we watched 3 and loved them. I would reccomend this pack if you like this type of movie.

Not what was advertised in the slightest. Only one movie (Too Young too Die) out of the 8 listed in the description turned out to be on the discs. Other random and bad movies made up the remaining 7 movies. Pretty bad that the discs don't even match the cover of the DVD case. Do not recommend at all. Very unsatisfied.
